  Source:
    Title: Divâni Shamsi Tabriz
    Locus: XLIV
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=Solar Symbolism
Commentary: Shamsi Tabriz means ‘Sun of Tabriz’.
---
From the Sun who is the glory of Tabriz seek future bliss,

For he is a sun, possessing all kinds of knowledge, on the spiritual
throne.
